                     <interp inst="t17780603-4-off14" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17780603-4-off14" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a silver tankard, value 5 l. a silver pint mug, value 40 s. two silver salts, value 30 s. a silver pepper box, value 15 s. and two salts, value 10 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17780603-4-person70">
                        John
                         Darby
                     <interp inst="t17780603-4-person70" type="surname" value="Darby"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17780603-4-person70" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17780603-4-person70" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , in the dwelling-house of the said John
            </rs>, March 16th.</p>
               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t17780603-4-victim72" type="victimName">
                     JOHN
                      DARBY
                  <interp inst="t17780603-4-victim72" type="surname" value="DARBY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17780603-4-victim72" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17780603-4-victim72" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
